21#ifndef GCC_REALGMP_H
22#define GCC_REALGMP_H
23
24#include <mpfr.h>
25#include <mpc.h>
26
27/* Convert between MPFR and REAL_VALUE_TYPE. The caller is
28 responsible for initializing and clearing the MPFR parameter. */
29
30extern void real_from_mpfr (REAL_VALUE_TYPE *, mpfr_srcptr, tree, mp_rnd_t);
31extern void real_from_mpfr (REAL_VALUE_TYPE *, mpfr_srcptr,
32 const real_format *, mp_rnd_t);
33extern void mpfr_from_real (mpfr_ptr, const REAL_VALUE_TYPE *, mp_rnd_t);
34
35#if (GCC_VERSION >= 3000)
36 /* For compatibility with mpfr 2.4 and earlier, we want to only use
37 GMP_RND*. */
38 #pragma GCC poison MPFR_RNDN MPFR_RNDZ MPFR_RNDU MPFR_RNDD
39#endif
40
41#endif /* ! GCC_REALGMP_H */
